ID: Ch3-Second-Easy
TEXT:

...easy. Easier than I thought it would be. I was afraid I'd hesitate at the very last moment, but the thought never crossed my mind. My hands and my body just instinctively moved the way they should have, and there were no awkward movements. This is a relief. I'll likely have to kill a lot more people before this tournament is over. It's good to know it isn't going to affect me.

