choice("Use the hilt of the dagger to knock him out", Ch3-First-Knock, v_current_scene = Ch3-First-Knock)


ID: Ch3-Decide-Killed
TEXT:

I take the liberty of swiping the ammunition of the first guy I took out, and go on my way, without looking back.

The first thing I need to decide now is what I'm planning to do with all of the crossbowmen I meet from this moment onward.

