ID: Ch3-Final-decision
TEXT:

Finally, I need to decide whether I want to go directly for the leader, or dispatch his troops first. If I capture the leader, then there's a chance I could persuade him to call off the attack, and end the fight sooner. However, if I fail to capture him, I'll only succeed in making myself the main target of his whole army.

